    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a reliable ride that's full of character? This car is in honest, fair condition and has plenty of life left for its next owner! While it shows some typical wear and tear from its adventures on the road, it remains a dependable choice for your daily commute or weekend errands. Get a great vehicle at a fantastic price!",
